  "texts": [
    "Zhu et al. [112] maximized the sensing SINR subject to the constant modulus and QoS constraints via optimizing the transmitted waveform.",
    "Liu et al. [114] investigated the IRS-aided ISAC system, where the transmitted waveform and phase-shift at IRS were jointly designed to maximize the sensing SINR.",
    "Considering the clutter, Wu et al. [173] designed a dualfunctional constant waveform for ISAC networks.",
    "Wang et al. [174] deployed an IRS to assist the ISAC system, and the beampattern mismatch was minimized via joint transmitted waveform and phase-shift optimization.• Communication-oriented design.",
    "The communication performance can be maximized subject to the sensing constraints for communication-oriented one."
  ]
}